%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d1af1a120e61d4046b725d4bf4f573bf, type: 3}
  m_Name: 03_Hub_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SimpleDialogueSequenceSO
  defaultTypingSfx: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 41c6af3979137354d8337f0d8b3c3e28, type: 3}
  defaultTypingSfxVolume: 0.4
  multiplyTypingByMasterVolume: 1
  multiplyTypingByAudioListenerVolume: 0
  masterVolumePrefsKey: settings_masterVolume
  autoCreateMasterPrefsKeyIfMissing: 1
  defaultMasterVolumeIfMissing: 1
  tutorialBeforeDialogue: {fileID: 0}
  tutorialAfterDialogue: {fileID: 0}
  tutorialLinksPerLine: []
  autoAdvanceByDefault: 0
  defaultAutoAdvanceSeconds: 0.8
  allowSkipAutoAdvanceWait: 1
  lines:
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: 'You''re lucky that you found me friend! '
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: Since I can help you return to your original world!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: Scattered across the DataSpace are what I call "key shards"...
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: 'They are the keys that will help you open a portal back to where you need
      to go! '
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: However they won't just appear to you that easily...
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 725ae35eec287b445a46259bfbf2c077, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 4
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: You see those huge folders?
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 725ae35eec287b445a46259bfbf2c077, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 4
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 
    text: '*You nod'
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 1
    emotion: 4
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: Those are actually portals that will take us to other worlds that exist
      in the DataSpace!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: Each world has their own inhabitants, which I call "Hosts".
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: They're like me!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: But less charismatic and lovable and nice and...
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 725ae35eec287b445a46259bfbf2c077, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 
    text: ...
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 1
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 
    text: ...
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 1
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 
    text: ...
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 1
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: Anyway...
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 725ae35eec287b445a46259bfbf2c077, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 4
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: 'To get the key shards you must first help the hosts with their own conundrums... '
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: After we help them solve these problems, the key shards will appear!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: Then, we'll return back here so i can open the portals to other worlds
      that contain other key shards...
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: And after you have all the required key shards you can finally return home!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 'Mouse '
    text: Does that sound good to you?
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: 
    text: '*You nod in agreement'
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 1
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: 'Great! Lets start with this first one! '
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3697e1d2fc2adcc48ba23a4aa5c8778e, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 2
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
  - speakerName: Mouse
    text: Just stand near the folder and it will let us in!
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 187bbd1323ce2ba45a31e48f24dfdac6, type: 3}
    clearPortraitIfNone: 0
    emotion: 0
    typingSfxOverride: {fileID: 0}
    typingSfxVolume: 0
    choices: []
    autoAdvanceSeconds: -1
